	<title>Hidden toolbar in most recent browser window as a target</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">User-Agent:       Mozilla/5.0 (Windows; U; Windows NT 5.2; en-GB; rv:1.7.8) Gecko/20050511 Firefox/1.0.4
